d by standard first and second moment\nmethods.\n  Finally, we also obtain an improved lower bound of $1.36000n$ on the Max-Cut\nfor the random cubic graph or any cubic graph with large girth, improving the\nprevious best bound of $1.33773n$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Nov 2014 18:42:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Feb 2017 07:27:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-14"}
