op of those discussed previously were considered, but none fully\nexplains the detected correlation. In light of the complex issue discussed\nhere, we encourage the different follow-up teams to publish their activity\nindex values in the form of log($R'_{HK}$) index so that a comparison across\nstars and instruments can be pursued.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Nov 2014 21:03:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-26"}
