fecting the lipid\nbilayers which surround ion channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Nov 2014 01:27:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Nov 2014 01:46:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2015 05:24:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-10"}
